{"tid":2433610,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"_chloewmy 俾人包嘅最高境界就係當自己真係富二代","createTime":"2021-03-05T04:02:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T04:02:26.000Z","uid":370034,"like":9,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"5d929a112b56df7963707b1e9501309669ffdf2b","tid":2433610,"uid":370034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T04:02:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UdVeCic.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUdVeCic.png&h=6c2d406c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n_Chloewmy黃文彥<br />\n日日係IG扮富二代 但事實上係比有錢大陸仔包<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢仲好鍾意用老豆老母係大陸人嚟打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪咁樣人地就以為佢係大陸富二代 而唔係比人包嘅公屋妹？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eTQhUFc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeTQhUFc.png&h=0876f1a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/310JQdy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F310JQdy.png&h=e1f32909&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武肺啱啱爆仲特登係淘寶買口罩送俾大陸「同胞」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GKyPq9K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGKyPq9K.png&h=78a0ef2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n整容樣嚟講佢都算柒<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BmDO1aA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBmDO1aA.png&h=9ee0ea8e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H3wtgJW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH3wtgJW.png&h=d93df1a5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8ySsxhh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8ySsxhh.png&h=a0c371f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mb3coUM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMb3coUM.png&h=b0ffcc4c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YkrUCeM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYkrUCeM.png&h=583d2c9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n比人包之後就日日夜夜係屋企打卡又將老母著到成隻雀咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我真係未見過人係屋企咁樣喪打卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WLpKzwP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWLpKzwP.png&h=bc7ea21f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/96Q9LDv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F96Q9LDv.png&h=13017b08&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VCDn5Dw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVCDn5Dw.png&h=6d5b73c7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k5uFSix.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk5uFSix.png&h=aed2f3e7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AjU6NRT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAjU6NRT.png&h=a98519a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sFhW95n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsFhW95n.png&h=e9bf2899&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mcPuLDJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmcPuLDJ.png&h=ac963a99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8G6hz2p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8G6hz2p.jpg&h=5130f1a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n碌sugar daddy卡買完名牌連單一齊擺上ig<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AkGpWo1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAkGpWo1.png&h=36034397&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n比人包之前係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CrAqJVN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCrAqJVN.png&h=effeaec5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UdEOgJ2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUdEOgJ2.png&h=17de46a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bHk6trj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbHk6trj.jpg&h=26408601&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢度係佢間公屋<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X4eFShm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX4eFShm.png&h=8bcb8dfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雞真係雞 要專登拍條片影自己啲手鏈頸鏈<br />\n隔住個mon都feel到佢比人包啲虛榮心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BkunmTR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBkunmTR.png&h=c321cabc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o8ebfdS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo8ebfdS.png&h=1186dd00&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c420a66ebf4f425fc7dca6c7b4f24dbf0e0baba8","tid":2433610,"uid":77403,"like":8,"dislike":9,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T04:03:44.000Z","msg":"屌你老母pr 大家未撚推"},{"pid":"40d02f1d8e396c4e205b4937add6bf7f7480239b","tid":2433610,"uid":2419,"like":19,"dislike":8,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T04:04:27.000Z","msg":"開完又開 上次都冇人理就收皮啦"},{"pid":"aa0aa5bc74716f85b8cbbdaa772d3bea96e94d24","tid":2433610,"uid":370034,"like":45,"dislike":3,"score":42,"quote":{"pid":"40d02f1d8e396c4e205b4937add6bf7f7480239b","tid":2433610,"uid":2419,"like":19,"dislike":8,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T04:04:27.000Z","msg":"開完又開 上次都冇人理就收皮啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T04:21:07.000Z","msg":"我鍾意開咪開囉 關你咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家連登開po要你批准？"},{"pid":"8770ca1acc82f422a5e756c18f585ce938f67039","tid":2433610,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-